272
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:17,160
Ya, saya pun tak percayakan dia.

273
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:18,640
Dia juga mengangkat keningnya ke arahku.

274
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:23,280
Sukar untuk dipercayai bahawa
kita semua berjaya berkumpul di sini.

275
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,720
Saya mahu bermain permainan.
Ingin sertai?

276
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:25,680
- Ya.
- Sudah tentu.

277
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:26,920
- Jom.
- Jom main.

278
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,480
Saya menonton siri bertajuk...
Apa nama ia sekali lagi?

279
00:15:29,520 --> 00:15:31,640
Ia dipanggil 'Bertaruh...'

280
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,800
Apa sahaja.

281
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,440
Permainan itu dipanggil "Kadar Denyutan Jantung".

282
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,400
Kosongkan meja untuk saya.

283
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:38,320
- Baiklah, mari kita pergi.
- Apakah "Kadar Denyutan Jantung" itu?

284
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,520
- Baiklah. Kosongkan meja.
- Permainan jenis apa ini?

285
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:43,320
Betul.

286
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,380
Pertama.

287
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,880
Jay dan Ya, berikan saya jam pintar kamu.

288
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,020
Setiap seorang daripada kamu, berikan milik kamu kepadaku.

289
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:50,880
Apa kejadahnya?

290
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:52,560
Tidak mampu membeli jam tangan pintar?

291
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,840
Alamak. Ini semua diperlukan untuk permainan ini.

292
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:55,520
Baiklah.

293
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,720
Peraturannya mudah.

294
00:15:58,040 --> 00:16:00,320
Jawab soalan,
dan jika kadar denyutan jantung anda melebihi 100 bpm,

295
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,040
dari bawah ke atas.

296
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,400
- Sial!
- Yo!

297
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,520
- Faham?
- Qin, awak main-main ke?

298
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,840
- Menarik.
- Tidak.

299
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,920
- Apa? Awak tak main-main?
- Qin!

300
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:10,720
Kami hanya dapat melepak sekali-sekala sahaja.

301
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:11,620
- Ya.
- Main permainan ini, sila.

302
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:12,560
Tolong! Tolong!

303
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,600
- Ayuh.
- Jangan takut.

304
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:15,000
Baiklah. Biar saya tunjukkan permainan ini.

305
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,840
Ki, mainlah dengan saya.

306
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,160
- Saya?
- Ya, awak.

307
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,880
- Baiklah. Teruskan!
- Jom kita lihat.

308
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,040
Jom main Batu, Kertas, dan Gunting.

309
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:25,160
Pemenang pergi dahulu.

310
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:27,000
Batu, kertas, gunting, tembak!

311
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,420
- Saya menang!
- Awak yang pertama.

312
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,440
Baiklah.

313
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,900
- Berikannya kepada saya.
- Ya?

314
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:37,240
Apabila anda dipukul di hadapan semua orang
di perhimpunan pagi,

315
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,840
awak malu, kan?

316
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,480
Awak ketawa kuat sangat, Jay.

317
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:48,200
Ha, ia bawah 100 bpm, bodoh.

318
00:16:48,680 --> 00:16:49,540
Giliran saya.

319
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,720
Pisau...

320
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,400
Oh, Dao...

321
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,920
Kau kata kau dah tinggalkan dia,

322
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,520
tapi sebenarnya
sebaliknya, bukan?

323
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:01,840
Apa?!

324
00:17:02,020 --> 00:17:04,160
- Aduh!
- Apa sebenarnya?

325
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,359
- Jelaskan diri anda.
- Wah.

326
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:06,760
Apa kebenarannya?

327
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,240
Ia 110 bpm. Awak kalah, bodoh!

328
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:11,160
- Atas sebab tertentu!
- Atas sebab tertentu!

329
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:15,800
Chug! Chug! Chug!

330
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:21,060
Baiklah. Siapa seterusnya?

331
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,000
Awak?

332
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:24,319
Saya keluar. Saya sia-sia. Bermain tanpa saya.

333
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,359
Jay, kau tak boleh main game ni.
Kau penuh dengan rahsia.

334
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:28,119
- Wah!
- Teruskan.

335
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:29,560
Saya akan bermain.

336
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,360
- Dengan siapa dia bermain-main?
- Tapi dengan satu syarat.

337
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:35,640
Saya bermain dengan Qin.

338
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,520
Sial.

339
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,160
Sheesh.

340
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:40,480
Apa?

341
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:42,680
Awak takut awak akan kalah?

342
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:44,800
Atau takut awak akan mengalah dengan perasaan awak?

343
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:46,520
Sial!

344
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:48,560
Dia sedang mengejeknya.

345
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:50,160
Jika anda tidak berminat untuk permainan ini,

346
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:51,560
tak apa.

347
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,920
Semua orang akan tahu bahawa

348
00:17:54,840 --> 00:17:56,000
awak masih merindui saya.

349
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,440
- Alamak!
- Wah!

350
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,640
Betul ke?

351
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,800
Dia terlalu mementingkan dirinya sendiri.

352
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:05,760
Dia tidak memberi Qin pilihan lain.

353
00:18:09,980 --> 00:18:10,920
- Saya masuk.
- Mari kita mulakan!

354
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,640
- Wah!
- Semangatnya!

355
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,840
- Malam ini menyeronokkan.
- Perlawanan yang hebat.

356
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,760
Baiklah. Buat ia kemas dan ketat.

357
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,600
Kau enggan menerima cintaku

358
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,520
sebab awak ada masalah komitmen, bukan?

359
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,200
Sial...

360
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:35,920
- Sial...
- Soalan pertama ini sukar.

361
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:40,720
Saya rasa tidak.

362
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:45,920
Awak sengaja buat saya terbayang, kan?

363
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:48,480
Wah!

364
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,360
Saya sedang menyediakan satu gambar khas untuk awak.

365
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,600
Ia sedang naik! Alamak!

366
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,800
Teddy yang aku bagi kau...

367
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:03,520
Awak masih pegang teguh, kan?

368
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:05,680
- Soalan apa?!
- Alamak!

369
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,280
- Aduh!
- Apa reaksinya?

370
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:10,160
Api lama sedang dihidupkan semula!

371
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,520
Ia sedang menunggu untuk dihidupkan semula!

372
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,800
♫Orang yang datang selepasnya♫

373
00:19:13,840 --> 00:19:15,680
- Apa?
- Hei, bukan itu sahaja.

374
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,440
Kau kembali untukku sekarang

375
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:34,840
sebab sayang kalau kehilangan saya, kan?

376
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:37,000
- Whoa.
- Aduh.

377
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:38,960
- Alamak!
- Sayang sekali.

378
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,760
Tutup...

379
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:41,360
- Ia semakin hampir.
- Awak nak bergambar sekarang?

380
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,080
- Whoa! Whoa!
- Ia sangat dekat!

381
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:44,500
- Dekat sangat, Tiw!
- 99 bpm?! Alamak!

382
00:19:44,540 --> 00:19:45,600
- Oh? Tiw?
- Ia mencecah 100 bpm.

383
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,720
Awak akan kalah!

384
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,480
Awak tanya saya tu

385
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:55,600
sebab awak masih minat saya, kan?

386
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:57,200
- Ah!
- Sial?!

387
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,680
- Apa yang akan berlaku?
- Terus ke intinya.

388
00:19:58,720 --> 00:20:00,080
- Oh? Ia sedang naik.
- Bukan main-main.

389
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,760
Oh? Jom mulakan!

390
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:22,440
Wah! Wah! Wah!

391
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:24,600
- Aduh!
- Mari kita mulakan!

392
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:27,160
Keadaan telah berubah!

393
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:35,480
Chug! Chug! Chug!

394
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:38,040
Chug...

395
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,720
- Oh...
- Chug...

396
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:41,160
Hei.

397
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:42,620
Jujurlah.

398
00:20:42,660 --> 00:20:45,120
Adakah kamu berdua masih mempunyai perasaan yang sama?

399
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,080
- Saya bergurau.
- Permainan dah tamat, kan?

400
00:20:55,080 --> 00:20:55,840
Awak nak pergi mana?

401
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:57,600
Jom bincang di luar.

402
00:20:58,580 --> 00:20:59,720
Kita tak ada apa-apa nak bincang.

403
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:01,920
Kita boleh berbual di meja awak.

404
00:21:07,060 --> 00:21:08,000
Mengapa menimbulkan masalah?

405
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:08,880
Apa?

406
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,760
Tak boleh ke saya duduk di meja awak?

407
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:20,400
Oh...

408
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:22,280
Ke mana dia nak bawa Qin?

409
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:23,960
Duang, inilah saatnya.

410
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,280
Kejar mereka.

411
00:21:25,520 --> 00:21:26,080
Hei.

412
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,840
Saya rasa ini bukan masanya.

413
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:29,280
Biarkan mereka bercakap.

414
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:31,200
Biar Duang yang selesaikan semuanya nanti.

415
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:34,480
Saya tidak fikir Qin seorang yang tidak rasional.
Fikirkanlah.

416
00:21:35,200 --> 00:21:36,080
Laman web...

417
00:21:36,320 --> 00:21:38,080
Dia tak boleh berputus asa.

418
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,300
Jika mereka berdamai,

419
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,920
Jadi siapa Duang dalam hubungan ini?

420
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,740
- Saya setuju dengannya.
- Hah?

421
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,920
Saya dah beritahu awak.

422
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,680
Ada dua syarat untuk aku
berhenti mengejar hati Qin.

423
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,400
Jika dia mahu kembali
dengan pemilik teddy itu,

424
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:53,440
kalau begitu saya akan keluar dari permainan ini, kan?

425
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:58,200
Sial.
Awak dipanggil kekasih hati ada sebabnya.

426
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,440
Adakah ini benar-benar keputusan anda?

427
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:03,440
Duang, tahanlah.

428
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,520
Siapakah awak?

429
00:22:04,840 --> 00:22:05,640
Apa yang awak cakap ni?

430
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:08,120
Siapa awak ni?
Saya tak kenal siapa ni.

431
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:09,940
Duang yang saya kenal

432
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:11,760
sentiasa berjuang hingga ke akhirnya.

433
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:13,640
Hei.

434
00:22:13,980 --> 00:22:14,960
Dengar cakap saya.

435
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:19,000
Jika anda tidak mahu menjadi anak anjing yang sedih
seperti yang dikatakan Pae,

436
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,480
